<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 12:12:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>报告：哈尼亚遇刺后希腊“高度戒备”针对以色列目标的袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-08-03/ty-article/greece-on-high-alert-for-attack-against-israeli-targets-after-haniyeh-assassination/00000191-1754-d68e-a79b-5fd5abee0000</link><description>据希腊《Kathimerini》报纸报道，希腊当局正在与外国情报机构联系，了解有关雅典以色列或犹太人目标遭受袭击的威胁加剧的报道。</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 10:18:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-08-03/ty-article/greece-on-high-alert-for-attack-against-israeli-targets-after-haniyeh-assassination/00000191-1754-d68e-a79b-5fd5abee0000</guid></item><item><title>报道：以色列摩萨德雇佣伊朗特工在哈马斯头目哈尼亚的房间里放置炸药</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/report-israels-mossad-hired-iranian-agents-to-plant-explosives-in-hamas-chiefs-room/00000191-16fa-db7e-a99d-1efa23980000</link><description>伊朗消息人士告诉《每日电讯报》，负责高级官员安全的革命卫队特工在哈马斯领导人被杀的德黑兰宾馆的另外两个房间里安放了爆炸装置</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 07:41:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/report-israels-mossad-hired-iranian-agents-to-plant-explosives-in-hamas-chiefs-room/00000191-16fa-db7e-a99d-1efa23980000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗：将在“适当的时间、地点和方式”对哈马斯头目被杀进行“严厉”的报复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article-live/haniyeh-killing-carried-out-by-mossad-hired-iranian-agents-u-s-moves-warships-to-mideast/00000191-155d-dba6-a59d-175f1a530000</link><description>报道：黎巴嫩南部车辆袭击造成 1 人死亡 ■ 纽约时报：伊朗因哈马斯领导人哈尼亚在德黑兰遇刺而逮捕了超过 24 人 ■ 巴勒斯坦人报告称，约旦河西岸图尔卡尔姆的车辆袭击造成 5 人死亡，其中包括哈马斯指挥官 ■美国国防部长下令向中东地区派遣海军巡洋舰和驱逐舰</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 01:35:56 GMT</pubDate><gu