rity-guards-are-palestinian-heres-why-thats-a-hopeful-development/00000191-143b-d116-a9db-dc7f45130000</guid></item><item><title>高级官员表示，以色列国防部长认为内塔尼亚胡对加沙协议不感兴趣</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/israeli-defense-chiefs-believe-netanyahu-isnt-interested-in-gaza-deal-top-official-says/00000191-14a0-d4cf-afb5-5cf5a8aa0000</link><description>以色列谈判小组的高级成员描述了内塔尼亚胡和高级国防官员之间在人质交易上的“分歧”；电视报道援引了总理指责他们太“软弱”的激烈交锋</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 20:15:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/israeli-defense-chiefs-believe-netanyahu-isnt-interested-in-gaza-deal-top-official-says/00000191-14a0-d4cf-afb5-5cf5a8aa0000</guid></item><item><title>由于地区紧张局势和价格飙升，这些航空公司削减了飞往以色列的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/these-are-the-airlines-cutting-flights-to-israel-as-regional-tensions-and-prices-skyrocket/00000191-1457-db7e-a99d-1edf0f6b0000</link><description>到目前为止，所有为以色列服务的美国航空公司以及几家欧洲航空公司都已暂停航班。以色列旗舰航空公司以色列航空维持正常航班，但票价却飙升</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 19:31:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/these-are-the-airlines-cutting-flights-to-israel-as-regional-tensions-and-prices-skyrocket/00000191-1457-db7e-a99d-1edf0f6b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队如何播下 10 月 7 日灾难的种子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-israels-army-sowed-the-seeds-of-its-october-7-disaster/00000191-13ba-db7e-a99d-1fba4cca0000</link><description>双桅船。盖伊·哈祖特 (Guy Hazoot) 将军的新书强调了 10 月 7 日哈马斯的傲慢和自满。同样的缺点是否会在与真主党或伊朗的更广泛战争中阻碍以色列？</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 18:32:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-israels-army-sowed-the-seeds-of-its-october-7-disaster/00000191-13ba-db7e-a99d-1fba4cca0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第301天：美国官员称伊朗可能使用代理人进行报复性攻击</title>